      objectReference: {fileID: 1681095106}
    - target: {fileID: 8380478931517338330, guid: a158166407669584697fa60594eb8c22,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogue.Array.size
      value: 13
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8380478931517338330, guid: a158166407669584697fa60594eb8c22,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogue.Array.data[0]
      value: '{panting slightly} See that was easy, nothin new.'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8380478931517338330, guid: a158166407669584697fa60594eb8c22,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogue.Array.data[1]
      value: Wow that was quick
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8380478931517338330, guid: a158166407669584697fa60594eb8c22,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogue.Array.data[2]
      value: Course it was. It's not like these things are smart. They may look human,
        but trust me they're not
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8380478931517338330, guid: a158166407669584697fa60594eb8c22,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogue.Array.data[3]
      value: Oh, what are they then?
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8380478931517338330, guid: a158166407669584697fa60594eb8c22,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogue.Array.data[4]
      value: Empty corrupted husks that linger. Just like me on a Friday night.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8380478931517338330, guid: a158166407669584697fa60594eb8c22,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogue.Array.data[5]
      value: '{chuckles} Wouldn''t that make you a zombie'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8380478931517338330, guid: a158166407669584697fa60594eb8c22,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogue.Array.data[6]
      value: '{chuckle} Nah, that would be me the morning after.'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8380478931517338330, guid: a158166407669584697fa60594eb8c22,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogue.Array.data[7]
      value: '{Static cuts through the radio}'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8380478931517338330, guid: a158166407669584697fa60594eb8c22,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogue.Array.data[8]
      value: I.......nse ....u....o...
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8380478931517338330, guid: a158166407669584697fa60594eb8c22,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogue.Array.data[9]
      value: Woah what was that?
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8380478931517338330, guid: a158166407669584697fa60594eb8c22,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogue.Array.data[10]
      value: Probably some radio interference Don't worry about it
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8380478931517338330, guid: a158166407669584697fa60594eb8c22,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogue.Array.data[11]
      value: I.......nse ....u....o...
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8380478931517338330, guid: a158166407669584697fa60594eb8c22,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogue.Array.data[0].dialogueName
      value: Watch
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8380478931517338330, guid: a158166407669584697fa60594eb8c22,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogue.Array.data[0].dialogueText
      value: Heads up boss, I just got a massive reading ahead. I'm guessing it's
        something big in there
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8380478931517338330, guid: a158166407669584697fa60594eb8c22,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogue.Array.data[1].dialogueName
      value: Hunter
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8380478931517338330, guid: a158166407669584697fa60594eb8c22,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogue.Array.data[1].dialogueText
      value: <b><i>*scoffs*</i></b> No problems. I'll deal with it like the rest,
        Haven't died yet
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8380478931517338330, guid: a158166407669584697fa60594eb8c22,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogue.Array.data[2].dialogueName
      value: Priest
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8380478931517338330, guid: a158166407669584697fa60594eb8c22,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogue.Array.data[2].dialogueText
      value: 'I asked you to leave. And instead, you continued. You spiteful, pitiful
        creature. The product of poor parenting, no doubt. '
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8380478931517338330, guid: a158166407669584697fa60594eb8c22,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogue.Array.data[3].dialogueName
      value: Priest
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8380478931517338330, guid: a158166407669584697fa60594eb8c22,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogue.Array.data[3].dialogueText
      value: 'For such a pitiful creature, you are persistent.  No matter.  Ahead
        of you lies one of my most loyal followers and dearest friends. A man of
        true honor and justice. He will protect us from your evil. '
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8380478931517338330, guid: a158166407669584697fa60594eb8c22,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogue.Array.data[4].dialogueName
      value: Hunter
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8380478931517338330, guid: a158166407669584697fa60594eb8c22,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogue.Array.data[4].dialogueText
      value: 'You know, for all his effort, he''s not exactly wounding me. '
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8380478931517338330, guid: a158166407669584697fa60594eb8c22,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogue.Array.data[5].dialogueName
      value: Watch
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8380478931517338330, guid: a158166407669584697fa60594eb8c22,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogue.Array.data[5].dialogueText
      value: Well, he is a ghost. maybe these were deep cuts back in his time?
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8380478931517338330, guid: a158166407669584697fa60594eb8c22,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogue.Array.data[6].dialogueName
      value: Hunter
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8380478931517338330, guid: a158166407669584697fa60594eb8c22,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogue.Array.data[6].dialogueText
      value: I guess, but they're just words <b><i>*sighs*</i></b>. dealt with his
        type before, all bluster and rigid rules.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8380478931517338330, guid: a158166407669584697fa60594eb8c22,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogue.Array.data[7].dialogueName
      value: Watch
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8380478931517338330, guid: a158166407669584697fa60594eb8c22,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogue.Array.data[7].dialogueText
      value: I'm guessing your dad?
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8380478931517338330, guid: a158166407669584697fa60594eb8c22,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogue.Array.data[8].dialogueName
      value: Hunter
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8380478931517338330, guid: a158166407669584697fa60594eb8c22,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogue.Array.data[8].dialogueText
      value: 'Yeah actually. <b><i>*higher voice of surprise*</i></b> Stern, religious
        man who demanded respect and obedience,  '
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8380478931517338330, guid: a158166407669584697fa60594eb8c22,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogue.Array.data[9].dialogueName
      value: Watch
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8380478931517338330, guid: a158166407669584697fa60594eb8c22,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogue.Array.data[9].dialogueText
      value: Ah sorry
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8380478931517338330, guid: a158166407669584697fa60594eb8c22,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogue.Array.data[10].dialogueName
      value: Hunter
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8380478931517338330, guid: a158166407669584697fa60594eb8c22,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogue.Array.data[10].dialogueText
      value: 'It''s fine. It''s in the past and I''d rather not talk about it now.
        It is what it is  '
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8380478931517338330, guid: a158166407669584697fa60594eb8c22,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogue.Array.data[11].dialogueName
      value: Watch
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8380478931517338330, guid: a158166407669584697fa60594eb8c22,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogue.Array.data[11].dialogueText
      value: I guess, but sometimes, holding on to the past keeps us trapped in the
        past. Either way, good luck in there.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8380478931517338330, guid: a158166407669584697fa60594eb8c22,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogue.Array.data[12].dialogueName
      value: Hunter
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8380478931517338330, guid: a158166407669584697fa60594eb8c22,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogue.Array.data[12].dialogueText
      value: Thanks. might as well get this over with
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    m_RemovedComponents: []
    m_RemovedGameObjects: []
    m_AddedGameObjects: []
    m_AddedComponents: []
  m_SourcePrefab: {fileID: 100100000, guid: a158166407669584697fa60594eb8c22, type: 3}
